quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  93,1,Waxaan ku dhaartay Barqada
  93,2,Iyo habeenka marka uu wax ku daboolo mugdigiisa
  93,3,"Rabbigaa kaama tagin (Muxammadow), mana uu kuu cadhoon"
  93,4,Oo hubaal waxa dambeeya baa kaaga khayr badan waxa hore u tagey
  93,5,"Oo dhowaan Rabbigaa baa deeq ku siin doona, marka waad raalli noqon"
  93,6,Miyuusan ku helin adigoo agoon ah oo ku hoyaadin
  93,7,Oo ku helin adigoo habowsan oo kuma hanuunin
  93,8,Oo ku helin adigoo caydh ah oo kuma hodmin
  93,9,"Ee ma agoonka, ha dhibin"
  93,10,"Oo ma kan wax weydiista, ha canaanan"
  93,11,"Oo ma xagga Nicmadda Rabbigaa, ka warran (oo ku mahdi)"